PatternDescription: Third-party library present in application lib folder (exploded project).
Fix: Dual-runtime: manage this dependency in Maven/Gradle and upgrade to a maintained Java-8-baseline release; validate on JDK 8 and JDK 21.
RemediationDescription: Replace exploded lib with build-managed dependency; choose a release that supports Java 8 and test on JDK 21.
